Class MediaSubTitle

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.mediarss.MediaSubTitle
public class MediaSubTitle extends Object
Optional element for subtitle/CC link. It contains type and language attributes. Language is based on RFC 3066. There can be more than one such tag per media element, for example one per language. Example: <media:subTitle type="application/smil" lang="en-us" href="http://www.example.org/subtitle.smil" />
